<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>174</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yé sū a wǒ jīn lái dào nǐ miàn qián,
 nǐ shì wǒ de yī kào, shì wǒ zuì hǎo de liáng bàn,\001
 cóng suì shǒu dào nián zhōng, nǐ tiān tiān dōu kàn gù,
 hēi yè dào bái tiān yǒu le nǐ cóng lái jiù bù gū dān,
 shāng xīn de shí hòu nǐ cā gàn wǒ lèi yǎn,
 ruǎn ruò wú lì de shí hòu, nǐ lái bǎ wǒ fú chān
 dú zuò jìng sī rén shēng mǎn le nǐ de ēn diǎn,</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ de cí ài jiǎng bù wán 迦南174</title>
</song>